Radiant Logistics, Inc., a third-party logistics company, provides technology-enabled global transportation and value-added logistics solutions primarily in the United States and Canada. It offers domestic, international air, and ocean freight forwarding services; and freight brokerage services, including truckload and intermodal services. In addition, the company provides logistics and supply chain services, including MM&D, CHB, and GTM services, as well as heavyweight and small package air services. It serves aviation and automotive, electronics and high tech, furniture and home furnishings, hospitality and gaming, humanitarian/NGO, industrial farming, and manufacturing and consumer goods; medical, healthcare, and pharmaceuticals; military and government; oil, gas, and energy; residential and white glove; retail, textile, apparel, and accessories; and trade shows, events, and advertising, as well as sporting goods industries. The company was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Renton, Washington.